-Our suggestion in using this template is to keep one excel file and update it with employee information as it becomes available. Then the current version can be uploaded at any time with all your current changes modified to our database. This removes the need to keep a record of information you've already submitted. Our software updates the database in either creating a new employee record or updates an existing employee record.
